This is the ChangeLog of the major changes in 0.8.
Use git-log to see the full changelog.

Build System:
	+ Changed from autotools to cmake
	+ no more dependency to libtool
	+ C++ is now a build dependency (used by cmake too)
	+ no LD_LIBRARY_PATH needed anymore
	+ new build variant: libelektra-full (dynamic Library with everything statically included)

Languages:
	+ Core is now Ansi C
	+ C++ can now be used for plugins
